TabMaster is a Chrome extension that offers a simplified way to manage and navigate your browser tabs. With just a shortcut command, it displays a clear list of all your tabs and allows you to effortlessly close any tabs you no longer need. Improve your browsing efficiency with TabMaster.
Trip: A shortcut (Alt + T) can be used to hide the TabMaster icon when not in use.
